#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Appointment booking <strong>🗓️</strong></strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການຈອງນັດໝາຍ <strong>🗓️</strong></strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Assign Personnel</strong>: Assign maintenance tasks to specific "
"employees or teams, ensuring that the right person is handling the repair."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ມອບໝາຍບຸກຄະລາກອນ</strong>: ມອບໝາຍວຽກບຳລຸງຮັກສາໃຫ້ກັບພະນັກງານ ຫຼື ທີມງານສະເພາະ "
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າມີຄົນທີ່ເໝາະສົມເປັນຜູ້ຈັດການການສ້ອມແປງ."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Automate Your Reordering Process 🚀</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ສ້າງຂະບວນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ 🚀</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Check Stock Levels</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>ກວດສອບລະດັບສິນຄ້າໃນສາງ</strong>:"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Choose Your Vendors</strong>: Select the vendors you want to reorder"
" from. You can also add bulk pricing options to save time and money."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເລືອກຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານ</strong>: ເລືອກຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເພີ່ມ"
"ຕົວເລືອກລາຄາແບບຊື້ຫຼາຍເພື່ອປະຢັດເວລາ ແລະ ເງິນ."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Confirm Orders</strong>: When an order is confirmed, a delivery is automatically created in the Inventory app. This allows you to keep track of stock levels and ensure you have enough inventory for your daily\n"
"                        operations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຢືນຢັນຄຳສັ່ງຊື້</strong>: ເມື່ອຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຖືກຢືນຢັນ, ການຈັດສົ່ງຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດໃນແອັບ "
"ສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory). ສິ່ງນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕິດຕາມລະດັບສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ໝັ້ນໃຈໄດ້ວ່າມີສິນຄ້າພຽງພໍສຳລັບການດຳເ"
"ນີນງານປະຈຳວັນ."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Maintenance Requests</strong>: Easily generate maintenance "
"requests when equipment needs repair or servicing. These requests can be "
"categorized and prioritized based on urgency."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍບຳລຸງຮັກສາ</strong>: ສ້າງຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍບຳລຸງຮັກສາໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍເມື່ອອຸປະກອນຕ້ອງກ"
"ານການສ້ອມແປງ ຫຼື ບໍລິການ. ຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສາມາດຈັດໝວດໝູ່ ແລະ ຈັດລຳດັບຄວາມສຳຄັນຕາມຄວາມຮີບດ່ວນໄດ້."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Reordering Rules</strong>: Click on the Products menu and "
"select Reordering Rules. Here, you can set minimum and maximum quantities "
"for each product to trigger automatic reordering."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງກົດການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່</strong>: ຄລິກທີ່ເມນູ ສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ເລືອກ ກົດການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່. ຢູ່ບ່ອນນີ້, "
"ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຈຳນວນຕ່ຳສຸດ ແລະ ສູງສຸດສຳລັບສິນຄ້າແຕ່ລະຢ່າງເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Tailor-Made Subscriptions and Sell Products Effortlessly "
"🛒</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ສ້າງຊຸດສະມາຊິກແບບພິເສດ ແລະ ຂາຍສິນຄ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ 🛒</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define Equipment</strong>: Create detailed profiles for each piece "
"of equipment, including specifications, usage history,emplacement,  and "
"maintenance requirements."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ກຳນົດອຸປະກອນ</strong>: ສ້າງຂໍ້ມູນລະອຽດສຳລັບອຸປະກອນແຕ່ລະຢ່າງ, ລວມທັງຄຸນລັກສະນະ, ປະຫ"
"ວັດການໃຊ້ງານ, ສະຖານທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງ ແລະ ຂໍ້ກຳນົດໃນການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Effortlessly manage your Point of Sale 💵</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຈັດການຈຸດຂາຍ (POS) ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ 💵</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Effortlessly manage your eCommerce 💵</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຈັດການການຄ້າແບບອີເລັກໂຕຣນິກ (eCommerce) ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ 💵</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Equipment Definition and Maintenance Requests</strong> 🛠️🔧"
msgstr "<strong>ການກຳນົດອຸປະກອນ ແລະ ຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍບຳລຸງຮັກສາ</strong> 🛠️🔧"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you "
"should Import demo data and try the features described in this "
"article.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການທົດລອງການໃຊ້ງານຕົວຈິງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ທ່ານຄວນນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ (Demo "
"data) ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ຟີເຈີຕ່າງໆທີ່ໄດ້ອະທິບາຍໄວ້ໃນບົດຄວາມນີ້.</strong>"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Integration with Employee Management</strong>: Link maintenance "
